title: Lombardi’s Week 17 Reactions and Regular-Season Wrap-up | GM Street (Ep. 375)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier wrap up the 2018 regular season discussing the finalized playoff picture, the ripple effects of the many firings around the league, and the main takeaway from what we saw on Sundays this season.
